title: FEB 04 2022 - BLM SHUTS DOWN FUNDRAISING IN CALIFORNIA
description:
BLM shuts down their online fundraising in California after Department of Justice warns they may lose their tax exempt status if they don’t file the proper forms, the Biden Administration refuses to not only provide any evidence of knowing about the ISIS leader blowing himself up but also anything involving the alleged Russia threats, Pelosi tells U.S. Olympians not to speak out against the Chinese Communist Party as they risk upsetting the Chinese government, and lastly, in Ottawa the truckers are settling in, but instead of setting up tents they have started building small homes for themselves. 




Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
